Late Badenian (middle Miocene): 
<emphasis id="B949EAD5FFB3FF99FB0AF9C46D50F948" box="[1063,1314,1647,1673]" italics="true" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">East Slovakian Basin</emphasis>
: Kuzmice (
<collectingCountry id="F32A7657FFB3FF99FFB2F9386976F96E" box="[159,260,1683,1710]" name="Slovakia" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Slovakia</collectingCountry>
) (
<bibRefCitation id="EFAC4B36FFB3FF99FE37F93F6990F96D" author="Svagrovsky, J." box="[282,482,1682,1711]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50" pagination="5 - 56" refId="ref145176" refString="Svagrovsky, J. (1958) Miocenne Pleurotomidae zapadokarpatskych panvi (Miozane Pleurotomidae der westkarpatischen Becken). Acta Geologica et Geographica Universitatis Comenianae, Geologica, 1, 5 - 56." type="journal article" year="1958">Švagrovský 1958</bibRefCitation>
, 1959, 1960a).
</paragraph>
